{"tid":917333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警署奇警】督察仆低瞓地 又關SORRY SIR事？","createTime":"2018-11-26T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T10:54:32.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea52108529931fe2b1fc456774cd2a31d8351939","tid":917333,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543226001_a5b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543226001_a5b9.jpg&h=993156c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因手持「SORRY SIR」紙牌而人氣爆燈的觀塘警署軍裝高級警員「番薯」，警隊盛傳他今日又有一「傑作」，而且比舉「SORRY SIR」紙牌更激。警隊群組今日流傳一張相片，相片中有一名身穿白色恤衫的督察躺在觀塘警署地牢一條走廊地上，盛傳與「SORRY SIR」有關。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，倒地的白衫督察隸屬觀塘警署行動及支援小隊。消息稱，「SORRY SIR」近年已調往行動及支援隊的內務工作，毋須外出巡邏。他今早申請假期時，被上司拒絕，兩人因此發生爭拗，其間白衫督察懷疑不慎跌倒地上，但消息指兩人沒有動過手。倒地的督察事後由救護車送往醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n「SORRY SIR」入職警隊約20年，綽號「番薯」，先後在多個警區、機動部隊（PTU）及衝鋒隊工作。他疑因與指揮官有過節，去年曾手持「SORRY SIR」字句的紙牌，在警署停車場雙膝跪地，成為城中熱話。今年5月，他又再在觀塘警署停車場舉起寫上「貪腐」標語示威。及至上月，他又再於觀塘警署外舉起寫上「SORRY SIR 我喺警察部嘅恥辱」標語示威，引起警署上下關注，並被人拍下照片輾轉流傳網上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543214772_e0ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543214772_e0ee.jpg&h=3e15d2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警隊群組今日流傳一張相片，相片中有一名身穿白色恤衫的督察，躺在觀塘警署一條走廊地上，盛傳與SORRY SIR有關。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543214864_c70b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543214864_c70b.png&h=1283fb87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【今年5月】SORRY SIR在觀塘警署停車場舉起「貪腐」標語。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543216631_a4dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543216631_a4dd.jpg&h=c6cb08ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【今年10月】SORRY SIR於觀塘警署外舉起寫上「SORRY SIR 我喺警察部嘅恥辱」標語示威。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181126/58959875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58959875&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=40e703a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58959875&h=a308aef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181126/58959875</a>"},{"pid":"e9b20fec0861d59ca4ebb32e54ffabfca27f0d43","tid":917333,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"好撚屈機 玩到謝又冇佢扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd02b3b7c4cbc689569075e051ab2cd69d594ba6","tid":917333,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9b20fec0861d59ca4ebb32e54ffabfca27f0d43","tid":917333,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"好撚屈機 玩到謝又冇佢扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}